DMA Test
--------
Targeted HW platforms:
 Broadwell-U
 Baytrail-T
For the platforms which have dma controllers.

Purpose:
 Test Memory to Memory copy through DMA controller

Driver source:
 ${Linux-kernel-tree}/drivers/dma/dw/platform.c

Required Linux kernel config options:
 CONFIG_DW_DMAC=y
 CONFIG_DMATEST=m

/!\ Use "make menuconfig" command to update Linux kernel config file and enable some potentially dependent options /!\
